                        <p>The authenticity, validity, and enforceability of this confirmation may be verified by the receiving bank through established interbank channels, including authenticated SWIFT communication, official telephone verification, or secure electronic correspondence.</p>
                        
                        <p>Note: This confirmation constitutes an operative banking instrument, subject to bank-to-bank verification via SWIFT MT199 (Free Format Message). It is fully assignable, transferable, and divisible, in accordance with the Uniform Customs and Practice for Documentary Credits (UCP), as issued by the International Chamber of Commerce, Paris (latest revision), and shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of France.</p>
                        
